Description: Command-line tool for file operations
 A powerful and user-friendly command-line utility that provides
 a set of tools for common file operations. It is designed to be
 simple to use while providing robust error handling and safety
 checks.
 .
 Features:
  * Create files (empty or with content)
  * Copy files with path validation
  * Combine multiple files into one
  * Safe file deletion with checks
  * Unicode support for file names
  * Comprehensive error handling
  * Path validation and sanitization
 .
 The tool is designed for both interactive use and scripting,
 with clear error messages and consistent behavior across
 different environments.